  <!-- EN: aiming accuracy -->
  <AimingAccuracy.label>瞄准精确度</AimingAccuracy.label>
  <!-- EN: How well a shooter can lead moving targets and estimate range in combination with the weapon's aiming efficiency.\n\nThe final modifier is calculated via this formula:\n(1.5 - aiming accuracy) / aiming efficiency\n\nLead error is calculated by multiplying this factor against total lead distance in cells. Range error is calculated by multiplying it against the total distance to the target divided by 4.\n\nAiming accuracy influences the the sway reduction during aimed shots. For example, at 75% aiming accuracy sway will be reduced to 25%. -->
  <AimingAccuracy.description>结合武器的瞄准效率，一个射手对移动目标的预判能力。\n\n最终判定数值根据以下公式计算：\n(1.5 - 瞄准精确度) / 瞄准效率\n\n预判误差：预判距离格数除以判定数值。\n射程误差：与目标的总距离除以4再除以判定数值。\n\n瞄准射击过程中的稳定性会受到瞄准精确度影响。例如，75%的瞄准精确度稳定性会被减弱至25%。</AimingAccuracy.description>
  
