  <!-- EN: melee armor penetration -->
  <MeleeArmorPenetration.label>近战护甲穿透</MeleeArmorPenetration.label>
  <!-- EN: Armor penetration in melee. Determines how much damage is lost to enemy armor. -->
  <MeleeArmorPenetration.description>近战护甲穿透数据。决定了近战情况下将会有多少的伤害值被敌人护甲阻挡。</MeleeArmorPenetration.description>
  
  <!-- EN: melee critical chance -->
  <MeleeCritChance.label>近战暴击几率</MeleeCritChance.label>
  <!-- EN: Base chance to critically hit a target in melee.\n\nThe final chance depends on the opponent's critical skill and equal opponents will always have a 10% chance to crit. -->
  <MeleeCritChance.description>近战攻击中产生致命一击的几率。\n\n最终数值取决于敌人相关技能等级，而敌人也会有10%的几率暴击。</MeleeCritChance.description>
  
  <!-- EN: melee dodge chance -->
  <MeleeDodgeChance.label>近战闪避几率</MeleeDodgeChance.label>
  <!-- EN: Chance to dodge a melee attack that would've otherwise hit. Characters will not dodge while aiming or firing a ranged weapon. -->
  <MeleeDodgeChance.description>闪避近身攻击或者其他物理击打的几率。\n\n（在瞄准时或使用远程武器开火时，角色无法进行闪避。）</MeleeDodgeChance.description>
  
  <!-- EN: melee parry chance -->
  <MeleeParryChance.label>近战招架几率</MeleeParryChance.label>
  <!-- EN: Base chance to parry a melee attack. When a parry is performed the equipped weapon or shield will take damage instead of the wielder. If the parrying pawn passes a critical chance check they will automatically riposte their attacker.\n\nThe final chance depends on the opponent's parry skill and equal opponents will always have a 20% chance to parry. -->
  <MeleeParryChance.description>招架近战攻击的几率。当一个招架被成功执行时，人物受到的攻击伤害将由他装备的武器或盾牌承受。如果成功执行招架的人物通过了一个特殊的数据检测，他们将对攻击者进行自动还击。最后的数据几率取决于对手的防守技巧，而同样的对手将会有20%的几率暴击。</MeleeParryChance.description>
  
  <!-- EN: reload speed -->
  <ReloadSpeed.label>换弹速度</ReloadSpeed.label>
  <!-- EN: The speed at which firearms are reloaded. -->
  <ReloadSpeed.description>重新装填弹药的速度。</ReloadSpeed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: suppressability -->
  <Suppressability.label>压制能力</Suppressability.label>
  <!-- EN: How susceptible this person is to suppression. Loss of consciousness and certain drugs can lower this value, making it harder to suppress this person. -->
  <Suppressability.description>表明了人物被压制的难易程度。适当的低意识状态和某些药剂能降低这个数值，使得人物更加难以被压制。</Suppressability.description>
  
